intended to be set by the project.
.sp
There is also an environment variable \fI\%CMAKE_LIBRARY_PATH\fP, which is used
as an additional list of search directories.
.sp
See also \fI\%CMAKE_SYSTEM_LIBRARY_PATH\fP and \fI\%CMAKE_PREFIX_PATH\fP\&.
.SS CMAKE_LINK_DIRECTORIES_BEFORE
