.sp
New in version 3.1.

.sp
True when the \fI\%CMAKE_SYSTEM_NAME\fP variable is set
to \fBWindowsCE\fP\&.
.SS WINDOWS_PHONE
.sp
New in version 3.1.

.sp
True when the \fI\%CMAKE_SYSTEM_NAME\fP variable is set
to \fBWindowsPhone\fP\&.
.SS WINDOWS_STORE
