.sp
New in version 3.7.

.sp
\fBTrue\fP when using \fI\%Xcode\fP generator.
.SS XCODE_VERSION
.sp
Version of Xcode (\fI\%Xcode\fP generator only).
.sp
Under the \fI\%Xcode\fP generator, this is the version of Xcode
