This setting is meaningful only when experimental support for \fBimport
std;\fP has been enabled by the \fBCMAKE_EXPERIMENTAL_CXX_IMPORT_STD\fP gate.
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
This variable is used to initialize the \fI\%CXX_MODULE_STD\fP property on
all targets.  See that target property for additional information.
