.sp
New in version 3.14.

.sp
Switch to enable generation of a global \fBautogen\fP target.
.sp
When \fBCMAKE_GLOBAL_AUTOGEN_TARGET\fP is enabled, a custom target
\fBautogen\fP is generated.  This target depends on all \fI\%AUTOMOC\fP and
